FBIS3-12206 "drnes039_o_94004" FBIS-NES-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 SYRIA Golan Demonstrations Denounce Hebron Attack JN2702145794 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1215 GMT 27 Feb 94 JN2702145794 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Villages and towns in the occupied Syrian Golan yesterday witnessed marches and demonstrations in solidarity with Palestinian brothers in the occupied Arab territories and in denunciation of the Hebron massacre. Syrian citizens raised banners and slogans denouncing the Israeli occupation authorities and the heinous massacre and demanding international protection from the provocation and arrogance of the settlers for Arab citizens.
